I",<p>В терминале пишем</p>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>defaults write com.apple.dashboard mcx-disabled <span class="nt">-boolean</span> YES
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Чтобы снова включить:</p>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>defaults delete com.apple.dashboard mcx-disabled
defaults write com.apple.dashboard mcx-disabled <span class="nt">-boolean</span> NO
</code></pre></div></div>
